DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260520T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260520T210000
SUMMARY:Give 'Em the Arrow Again!  Ladies Night at the Archery Range
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma County Women's Wine Club (SCWWC)\nI'm super excited to 
 be able to offer another ladies' Archery night in Santa Rosa! If you've ev
 er had a curiosity about archery\, this is your chance to find out more wi
 th a fun\, interactive lesson.\n\nWe have reserved a special event with th
 e indoor range on a Wednesday evening. It will consist of a basic lesson\,
  and then we all get to practice shooting. Everyone will get ample time to
  practice\, as they have many lanes.\n\nThis event is focused on a less-co
 mpetitive\, relaxed\, and entertaining atmosphere. All skill levels are en
 couraged. All equipment is provided by them\, and we will probably get abo
 ut an hour or hour and a half to practice.\n\nI encourage everyone to brin
 g a bottle of wine or a snack to share with the rest of the group (We usua
 lly end up with a lovely charcuterie and wine spread for everyone to enjoy
 ). Closed toe shoes recommended.\n\nThere are 17 spots available\, guests 
 welcome. The ladies' group lesson and event is $30 person\, paid to the ra
 nge. Starting March 2025\, we ask that every attending member pay a $1 "sl
 ush" fund fee per event in addition to the regular fee so that we can buil
 d up our funds for club-related expenses\, which can be paid by Venmo or c
 ash.\n\nPlease only RSVP 'Yes' if you are able to make it\, hostess Dai Ph
 ipps will be collecting a $5 fee via Venmo to hold your spot. She will fol
 low up with everyone who RSVP's 'Yes' via direct message or you may pay th
 e $5 through the enclosed Venmo link. Returns cannot be accommodated after
  the Sunday before the event. Here is the link: www.venmo.com/Daima-Phipps
 \n\nThere is an attendance policy for all our events: if you No-Show to th
 ree events\, you may not attend events for the next three months. Please p
 ut this event in your calendar so you don't miss out or get dinged. A No-S
 how is when you are on the 'Going' list\, but do not show up.\n\nCheers\, 
 and hope to see you there!
